  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Wayside Train Monitoring System (WTMS) heat-detection event for a freight wagon.",
    "Architecture: the event references identifiers by URI — GTIN in epcList, GLN in readPoint/bizLocation, party GLN in source/destination. Model-, location-, and party-level master data is served by the GS1 Digital Link / Web Vocabulary resolver when those URIs are dereferenced; it is NOT embedded in the event.",
    "masterDataAvailableFor carries ONLY item/lot-level master data (e.g. countryOfOrigin, regulatoryInformation, harvestDate, EUDR plot geolocation). ilmd carries lot/instance data of the items this event creates. Observation extensions sit at event level.",
    "",
    "  GS1-Extensions: rail=https://gs1-epcis-reg.org/rail/voc/data#, oec=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952. Wagon EPC encodes a rail vehicle identifier via GIAI-style"
  ],
